git stash -  saves your local change temporarily in a commit
             As you fetch remote changes
             git pull


git stash pop - restore your files from the storing area
               - And deletes files from storage area

git stash apply - restores changes without deleting changes from storage area

git stash push -m "saving with a message" - storing your files with a message

git stash list - list all stashed changes in LIFO format

git stash drop stash@{0} - drop a particular stash commit/change from storage area

git stash clear - clear all stash

git stash -u -  includes untracked files

git stash -a -  Includes also the ignored files